title: Elbow Grease Pink All Purpose Degreaser Spray – Extra Large (1 Litre) | Removes Grease & Oil from Kitchen & Bathroom Surfaces, Outdoor, Vehicles & Fabrics
features: UNIQUE FORMULA: This unique, pink solvent-free formula is gentle and safe to use for removing grease spots from delicate and coloured fabrics, yet tough enough to clean vehicle parts and metal surfaces including alloy wheels

VERSATILE USE: The Elbow Grease Pink All-Purpose Degreaser is perfect for removing tough grease stains from kitchen and bathroom surfaces, fabrics, carpets, plastics and even engines and machinery. The spray has 1000s of uses for all around your home

FRESH SCENT: The Elbow Grease Pink All-Purpose Degreaser not only keeps the surface perfectly clean and grease-free, but it leaves a heavenly fresh Pink Blush scent in your kitchen and bathroom that lasts for hours
ABOUT THE PRODUCT: Elbow Grease Pink 1L bottle. Solvent-free. Not suitable for wood. Vegan friendly
description: Product Description Tackle grease like a pro with the Elbow Grease All-Purpose Degreaser, now in a special limited edition Pink Blush! This powerful cleaner is formulated to remove tough grease and oil from all types of surfaces and materials around the home, from the kitchen to the bathroom, and even outdoor areas. The solvent-free, safe-to-use formula is tough on stains yet gentle enough for fabrics, coloured surfaces, and more. Made to handle your dirtiest jobs, this 1-litre, extra-large bottle of Elbow Grease spray delivers incredible cleaning power while leaving behind a refreshing grapefruit scent. Use this miracle spray as a kitchen cleaner, oven cleaner for heavy-duty messes, or even as an induction hob and air fryer cleaner. This multipurpose solution is ideal for households where versatility and powerful cleaning are key, making it a true household essential. Experience the deep clean Elbow Grease is known for and enjoy the unique Pink Blush scent that leaves your spaces smelling fresh and inviting.
